Problem: The CLI exhibits several correctness and UX issues


    Mixed stdout output: Human-readable banners and progress lines are printed to stdout alongside JSON/YAML output, which corrupts machine-readable streams when piping. Additionally, markdown/table outputs interleave with progress messages.
   

Proposed solution:

    Separate channels: write all progress/info to stderr, and emit pure JSON/YAML to stdout with no decoration. Add --quiet and --no-banner flags.
 
